unittitle_ssm: Peter Brandt photographs of the TWA Flight Center
abstract_ssm: The collection includes 47 8x11 inch photographs by Peter Brandt of the TWA Flight Center at Kennedy Airport. 10 of the photographs are in color; all are captioned on the back and include the photographer's stamp; and most are of the terminal's interior, with some exterior views.
